data.title: Marines TV
data.meta_description: Educators from 4th Marine Corps District experience the 2023 Educators Workshop at Marine Corps Recruit Depot Parris Island, S.C.   The purpose of the workshop is to inform high school educators and community influencers  about the process of becoming a United States Marine and to raise awareness of the opportunities and benefits for qualified individuals in the Marine Corps.  (U.S. Marine Corps video by Cpl. Bernadette Pacheco)
data.text: Educators from 4th Marine Corps District experience the 2023 Educators Workshop at Marine Corps Recruit Depot Parris Island, S.C.
